channel.title: How do I set my player-made skill in the music/empty tab?
channel.description: Can someone tell me how to set my skill in the Music tab or Tab 7 (Ancients/Empty Tab)? I tried, but didnt work. And I also tried giving my skill a number (4156) in a different section of the client.java and it worked, but it didnt appear. So I wanna put a Construction skill there so you can click on the writing and make an object.
